{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"cursor","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/cursor","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n<p>The <code>cursor</code> attribute specifies the mouse cursor displayed when the mouse pointer is over an element.</p>\n<p>This attribute behaves exactly like the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/cursor\"><code>css cursor</code></a> property except that if the browser supports the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/cursor\"><code>&lt;cursor&gt;</code></a> element, you should be able to use it with the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#funciri\">&lt;funciri&gt;</a> notation.</p>\n<p>As a presentation attribute, it also can be used as a property directly inside a CSS stylesheet, see <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/cursor\"><code>css cursor</code></a> for further information.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Categories</th>\n      <td>Presentation attribute</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n      <td>\n        [[<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#funciri\">&lt;funciri&gt;</a>,]* [ <strong>auto</strong> | crosshair | default | pointer | move |\n        e-resize | ne-resize | nw-resize | n-resize | se-resize | sw-resize |\n        s-resize | w-resize| text | wait | help ]] | inherit\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Normative document</th>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/interact.html#CursorProperty\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following elements can use the <code>cursor</code> attribute</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#container_elements\">Container elements</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#graphics_elements\">Graphics elements</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.cursor","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/cursor/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/cursor\"><code>css cursor</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-02-04T07:16:02.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/svg/attribute/cursor","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/svg/attribute/cursor/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/614cd623fac41cbc68c54ef33b82dd4d5ebb04f7","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG Attribute reference"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/cursor","title":"cursor"}],"pageTitle":"cursor - SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics | MDN","noIndexing":false}}